defaultFWD members make an extensive contribution to the UK economy generating economic activity through the management and distribution of goods worth around £28billion per annum.
default 
defaultFWD member organisations include: P&amp;H; Bestway; 3663; Brakes; Costco
default (wholesale); Blakemore; Booker
default; Landmark Wholesale
default; Today’s Group
default. These members have 800 regional depots which employ 70,000 people up and down the country, serving every UK postcode, every day.
