defaultIn 2012 the wholesale sector 
defaultwas 
defaultvalued 
defaultat 
default£27.2bn, comprised of £6.5bn in delivered food services, £11.6bn in ‘cash &amp; carry’, and £9.1bn in delivered groceries. The wholesale sector is predicted to grow to £31bn in 2017, an increase of 13.8%.
